title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 5 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 5 2022
description:
Kash Patel, former DOD Chief of Staff and Deputy Assistant to President Trump, on how the deep state is hiding information Trump declassified and the latest in the Durham probe. Doocy questions Psaki. Would you hire Joe Biden to do anything? Fox's Dana Perino joins Clay and Buck, discusses her new book: Everything Will Be Okay. Johnny Depp/Amber Heard trial. C&B's moms will be on the show Friday. Leave a question for Clay and Buck's moms now on a dedicated line: 212-445-3969. We'll air the best ones on Friday!

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
